description: The Ballistic SG Series Case offers three layers of protection for your iPhone 5. The first and outermost layer is made of soft TPU which will help absorb the shock of a drop. In addition, this first layer is co-molded onto layer number two, which is made of a touch impact resistant polycarbonate. Last but not least, the third layer, which is the inner-most layer, is made of a soft silicone. This layer also includes Ballistic corners, which means all four corners have extra shock absorption where you need it the most.
